cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for improving the performance of deep neural networks on vision-based tasks in urban driving scenes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning frameworks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with autonomous vehicles, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics). The paper involves the use of image to image translation techniques, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves the use of self-supervised learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
